457
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:17,740
You're usually a smart guy.

458
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:20,680
But when it comes to relationship, you act like an idiot.

459
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:23,880
I'm so worried about you.

460
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:49,380
Lin Xichi?

461
00:37:01,500 --> 00:37:03,400
Senior Ye.

462
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:10,840
That is... I have a question.

463
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:16,559
