00:37:16,559 --> 00:37:18,720
Tomorrow is the weekend.

465
00:37:18,720 --> 00:37:21,660
I'm wondering if you're available.

466
00:37:21,660 --> 00:37:24,400
Then, I'd like to treat you to a meal.

467
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:43,640
Just spit it out!

468
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:49,060
What kind of girl do guys usually like?

469
00:37:51,260 --> 00:37:52,939
Why are you suddenly asking me this?

470
00:37:52,939 --> 00:37:55,679
Don't bother knowing why! Just tell me now.

471
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:04,200
Guys usually prefer to use some numbers,

472
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:06,319
girls with long hair,

473
00:38:06,319 --> 00:38:08,600
girls who wear white dresses,

474
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:11,440
and know how to be coy.

475
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:13,920
Do all guys like that kind of girl?

476
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:18,340
In short, it's the ones that are the complete opposite style of yours.

477
00:38:20,700 --> 00:38:24,299
- What are you doing?
- You don't deserve to eat a meal but only dog food.

478
00:38:24,299 --> 00:38:26,680
You deserve only cat food.

479
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:31,180
- Why are you suddenly asking me this?
